Usefull Sql query and function

SQL Function
------------

1. Length
   Ex. Length('nizam');    Output= 5

2. Trim
   Ex. Trim(' remove start space or tab and end space or tab. ')
   Output =remove start space or tab and endspace or tab.|

3. Concat
   Ex. Concat('nizam','badhara') O=nizambadhara

4. Upper
   Ex. Upper('nizam').    O=UPPER
   
5. Lower
   Ex. Lower('Nizam').    O=nizam
